Setting up OBS in new PC:

- Countdown
- 
- [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=foaxPR1hmuI](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=foaxPR1hmuI)
    
- Download countdown from here
    
- [https://github.com/ashmanix/obs-plugin-countdown](https://github.com/ashmanix/obs-plugin-countdown)
    
- ![410](data:image/png;base64,)
    
- Download from here
    
- [Download](https://github.com/ashmanix/obs-plugin-countdown/releases/download/2.1.1/obs-plugin-countdown-2.1.1-windows-x64.zip)
    
- Copy folder to C:\ProgramData\obs-studio\plugins
    
- Open obs
    
- Docks, countdown
    
- Add a text in the desired scene
    
- In the countdown options select the timer text element from the scene .
    
- Press start on the timer and the text appears there.

# Keyboard shortbuts

- Set all hotkeys to turn off camera and mic to win shift q
    
- Win shit e starts recording and pauses/ unpauses
    

- Win shift r stops recording
